// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0038 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: af87e7bf-424f-5300-93f8-3e18ff2f92d7

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*")
